title: The Steve Wilkos Show Your Child Said Mommy Burned Me
description:
Your Child Said Mommy Burned Me 
--------------------------------

Doctors discover that a 2-year-old with a life-threatening head injury has cigarette burns covering her body; a 4-year-old tells doctors that his mother caused his three burn marks. 

Season number: 7 

Episode number: 21 

Air date: October 14, 2013
